      <h3>Printing Colors (CMYK)</h3>
      <p>
        When creating printed materials, such as shirts or posters, CMYK color mode is used instead of RGB.
        Please ensure that your graphics software is set to use CMYK. We also provide the corresponding RGB value
        based on an algorithmic CMYK to RGB conversion - however this may not be accurate.
      </p>
