    </section>
    <section id="typography">
      <h2>Typography</h2>
      <p>
        Presently, Helvetica Neue is used as our primary font for just about everything. Helvetica Neue Bold is used for
        logo wordmarks and headers, while Helvetica Neue Regular is used for body text.
      </p>
      <p>
        Consolas is used as the font for code and monospace purposes.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="user-interface">
      <h2>User Interface</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://fluent2.microsoft.design/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Microsoft Fluent 2</a> is
        the basis for most of our user interface design. For iconography,
        <a href="https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui-system-icons" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fluent Icons</a> are
        primarily used, along with <a href="https://github.com/microsoft/fluentui-emoji" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fluent Emoji</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="misc">
      <h2>Miscellaneous</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Unless being written out, dates should be written in <code>YYYY-MM-DD</code> format rather than ambiguous
          formats such as <code>MM-DD-YYYY</code> or <code>DD-MM-YYYY</code>
        </li>
        <li>
          Prioritize the usage of left-aligned content over center-aligned content. Avoid right-aligned content as much as possible.
        </li>
        <li>
          When using quotes, ensure that "straight quotes" are used instead of 	&#8220;smart quotes&#8221; in content.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
